The,IMN,Instituto,Meteorol,gico,Nacional,is,the,scientific,body,responsible,for,the,coordination,of,all,meteorological,activities,in,Costa,Rica,It,systematically,monitors,the,weather,in,order,to,promote,the,safety,of,air,navigation,and,prevent,hydrometeorological,disasters,The,IMN,API,provides,users,with,programmatic,means,for,getting,the,current,weather,as,well,as,near,and,long,term,forecasts,for,cities,or,regions,within,Costa,Rica,The,website,and,the,API,documentation,are,given,only,in,Spanish